  <entry>
    <title>《一只企鹅决定远行》</title>
    <link href="http://gaolileo.com/posts/AZSX6W.html"/>
    <id>http://gaolileo.com/posts/AZSX6W.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-28T02:50:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-28T03:10:10.809Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>企鹅也会发疯吗</p><p>他既不向觅食地前进</p><p>也不返回栖息地</p><p>他朝着远处的群山直冲过去</p><p>山在七十公里之外</p><p>一只像这样迷路或发狂的企鹅</p><p>离他该去得地方已经八十公里了</p><p>他朝着广袤大地的深处而去</p><p>还有五千公里的路要走</p><p>他终将难逃一死</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428111001251.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428111001251.png" alt="图片"></a></p><p>2015年8月29日 内蒙古 太仆寺旗</p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
