  <entry>
    <title>《八月二十九日晴》</title>
    <link href="http://gaolileo.com/posts/2A0CK5K.html"/>
    <id>http://gaolileo.com/posts/2A0CK5K.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-28T02:50:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-28T03:07:00.802Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>穿着拖鞋短裤</p><p>走在北京的大街</p><p>头顶是夏日的骄阳</p><p>身边不时卷起凉薄的风</p><p>老死的黄叶满天飞舞</p><p>和强悍的紫外线告别</p><p>除了风中夹杂的灰尘</p><p>这是北京最好的季节</p><p>活在这座城中的人</p><p>都爱它的分明</p><p>一年四季四种心情</p><p>它也用明晃晃的轮回昭示人们</p><p>时间将飞快</p><p>跟抽血似的让人心疼</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110649445.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110649445.png" alt="图片"></a></p><p>2017年5月30日 广西 桂林</p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
