  <entry>
    <title>《南国之冬》</title>
    <link href="http://gaolileo.com/posts/1AF7NCQ.html"/>
    <id>http://gaolileo.com/posts/1AF7NCQ.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-28T02:50:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-28T03:08:49.681Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>窗外有风啸叫，大雪肆虐</p><p>壁炉烧了一夜</p><p>火光撑起一个温暖的巢穴</p><p>我贪婪的摩擦双脚，血液滚烫</p><p>这一定是西伯利亚最后有补给的驿站</p><p>醒后我知道窗外不可能有雪</p><p>顶多是冰凉湿漉的墨绿</p><p>过去忍耐着枯燥的寒冬，憧憬南国和椰风</p><p>现在，冬天只在醒来的一瞬间</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110838260.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110838260.png" alt="图片"></a></p><p>2015年4月25日 尼泊尔 蓝毗尼</p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
