  <entry>
    <title>《囚禁》</title>
    <link href="http://gaolileo.com/posts/306BGGS.html"/>
    <id>http://gaolileo.com/posts/306BGGS.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-28T02:50:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-28T03:10:43.097Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>广州与关岛之间</p><p>大海深沉 ，明月高悬，白浪飞溅</p><p>普罗米修斯号，载着导弹和我们</p><p>一栋白房子，每人一张茧</p><p>太阳从未出现，永夜里目光荒诞</p><p>山丘上的草绿的晃眼，远处的海墨蓝</p><p>墙上床上布满藤蔓</p><p>就这样被囚禁在关岛数十年 </p><p>火山从未喷发</p><p>但包围我的海水，几如火焰</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428111031591.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428111031591.png" alt="图片"></a></p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
