    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>暑气未消秋已浓。</p><p>雁南飞，梯云纵。</p><p>西风意懒，紫霞镶万重。</p><p>千里穿行话相逢，来时梦，转头空。</p><p>烟花散作霓虹灯。</p><p>北国中，南国梦。</p><p>龙吟长调，情歌也峥嵘。</p><p>年年岁岁花相似，人不同，怕寒冬。</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110405237.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110405237.png" alt="图片"></a></p><p>2018年10月5日 泸沽湖 川滇界</p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
