  <entry>
    <title>《满江红》</title>
    <link href="http://gaolileo.com/posts/1C20853.html"/>
    <id>http://gaolileo.com/posts/1C20853.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-28T02:50:34.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-28T03:03:34.107Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/css/lightgallery.min.css" /><div class=".article-gallery"<p>掌灯无人睡，</p><p>平明少人醒。</p><p>灯红酒绿胯下，</p><p>金戈铁马獠牙。</p><p>彼一时，人神共赏，信笃天涯；</p><p>此一时，柔情死水，新人旧画。</p><p>纵使心如磐石，抵不过万人浮夸，</p><p>罢罢罢，哀乐之巅写年华。</p><p><a href="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110323129.png" title="图片" class="gallery-item"><img src="http://pic.gaolileo.com/640-20220428110323129.png" alt="图片"></a></p><p>2018年2月1日 后海 北京</p></div><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/lightgallery.js/1.0.1/js/lightgallery.min.js"></script><script>if (typeof lightGallery !== 'undefined') {        var options = {            selector: '.gallery-item'        };        lightGallery(document.getElementsByClassName('.article-gallery')[0], options);        }</script>]]></content>
    
    
